# Repo Navigation

## Architecture

- `design.md` -- architecture diagrams (Mermaid), component details, data flow, technology stack
- `AGENTS.md` -- agent guide with module map, error hierarchy, skill index, conventions

## Skills

Canonical location: `.agent/skills/` (each has SKILL.md + optional references/).
Cursor symlinks: `.cursor/skills/` points to `.agent/skills/` for discoverability.
Full index: see the "Available Skills" table in AGENTS.md.

## Tests

- `tests/` -- mirrors `src/` structure
- Markers defined in `pytest.ini`: `unit`, `slow`, `e2e`, `gpu_integration`, `integration`, `infrastructure`, `skip_in_ci`, `noautouse`
- Tests are auto-marked by directory (`tests/e2e/` -> `e2e`, `tests/gpu_integration/` -> `gpu_integration`, etc.)
- Shared fixtures: `tests/conftest.py`
- Stub data: `tests/test_data/`, `tests/stub_datasets/`, `tests/stub_tokenizer/`

## Config Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `pyproject.toml` | Package metadata, dependencies, extras (cpu/cu128/engine), uv config |
| `pytest.ini` | Test markers, pytest options, timeout, parallelism |
| `ruff.toml` | Ruff linting and formatting rules |
| `mkdocs.yml` | Documentation site config (MkDocs Material) |
| `.pre-commit-config.yaml` | Pre-commit hooks (ruff, ty, copyright, uv-lock) |
